_struct.entry_id ma-t3vr3-003
_struct.pdbx_model_details
;Predicted interaction between CCR4-NOT transcription complex subunit 1 (residue 1824 - 2376) and CCR4-NOT transcription complex subunit 3 (residue 607 - 753).

Model generated using AlphaFold2 with a 200 residue separation between the chains starting from a paired Multiple Sequence Alignment(pMSA).
;
_struct.pdbx_structure_determination_methodology computational
_struct.title 'Predicted interaction between CNOT1 (1824-2376) and CNOT3 (607-753)'

